high_descs: Turn right, walk to the wall, and then turn right towards the sink counter.
Pick up the lotion bottle farthest from you.
Turn around and walk towards the black bin on the floor next to the wall.
Place the bottle in the bin.
Turn around and walk back to the sink counter.
Pick up the other lotion bottle from the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the black bin on the floor next to the wall.
Place the bottle in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place the two lotion bottles from the sink counter into the black bin next to the wall.
